<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00017</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTIONALIZING A CONDITIONAL CASH TRANSFER PROGRAM, PROVIDING FOR THE AUTOMATIC INDEXATION OF CASH GRANTS AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Pantawid Pamilyang Pilipino Program (4ps) Act</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Institutionalizes the Pantawid Pamilyang Pilipino Program (4Ps) which is a human development measure of the national government administered by the Department of Social Welfare Development (DSWD) that provides conditional cash grants to the poorest of the poor, aimed at reducing, if not eradicating, the incidence of poverty in the country.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BIAZON, ROZZANO RUFINO B.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Welfare</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Roque (H.) (002 2016-07-26)</td><td>2. Fortun (004 2016-08-01)</td><tr><td>3. Alvarez (F.) (008 2016-08-09)</td><td>4. Sarmiento (C.) (024 2016-09-20)</td><tr><td>5. Alejano (095 2017-05-29)</td><td>6. Mercado (022 2017-09-11)</td><tr><td>7. Mendoza (000 2018-01-16)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Under deliberation by the Mother Committee on 2017-03-14</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Under deliberation by the Mother Committee on 2017-11-20</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp3. Under deliberation by the Mother Committee on 2017-12-05</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp4. Under deliberation by the Mother Committee on 2017-12-11</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp5. Under study by the Technic